S'Download one of the best Android eBook Readers now!\xe2\x98\x85The leading eBook application for the Android platform\xe2\x98\x85Pre-installed in 20+ different Smartphones and Tablets\xe2\x98\x8510+ million users from over 200 countriesDifferences between the Aldiko Book Reader Premium and the Aldiko Book Reader Free are: the Aldiko Book Reader Premium has highlights, notes and home widget features, gets faster update and does not contain advertisements.Features of the Aldiko Book Reader Free:\xe2\x9c\x94 Support EPUB, PDF formats as well as Adobe DRM encrypted eBooks.\xe2\x9c\x94 Support eBooks from public libraries.\xe2\x9c\x94 Fully-customizable reading experience: adjust font size, font type, font and background colors, margin, alignment, line spacing as well as brightness to best suit your preference. The Aldiko Book Reader also supports night-time reading.\xe2\x9c\x94 User-friendly interface: the Aldiko Book Reader supports both Android phones and tablets. You can create your own bookmarks anywhere in the book, rapidly jump to a different section of the book through the table of content.\xe2\x9c\x94 Advanced library management system: import your own EPUB and PDF files into the app to read them on the go; organize your eBooks by tags and collections. Aldiko will also remember your reading position automatically, bring you back to where you left off.\xe2\x9c\x94 In-app shopping experience: browse huge catalogs of eBooks, including best-sellers, new releases and classics (lots of them are FREE)\xe2\x9c\x94 Other cool features not to miss: global-text search in a book, dictionary, add your own favorite catalogs and many more\xe2\x9c\x94 Language localization: Aldiko Book Reader app supports English, \xe4\xb8\xad\xe6\x96\x87(\xe7\xae\x80\xe4\xbd\x93) \xe4\xb8\xad\xe6\x96\x87(\xe7\xb9\x81\xe9\xab\x94), Deutsch, Fran\xc3\xa7aise, Espa\xc3\xb1ol, Italiano, \xed\x95\x9c\xea\xb5\xad\xec\x9d\x98, Nederlands, Danske, \xce\xb5\xce\xbb\xce\xbb\xce\xb7\xce\xbd\xce\xb9\xce\xba\xce\xac, Bahasa Indonesia, Polski, Portugu\xc3\xaas, Finnish, Hungarian and Svenska.Aldiko Book Reader works on Android phones and tablets with Android version 2.2 or above.Recent changes:-Support for 7" tablet support, e.g. Nexus 7 -Faster PDF zooming and remember zoom level -Support importing .acsm files directly right inside the app -Faster book cover loading in library and in store -Enhanced security to protect your database in the app -Fixed issues downloading books from local libraries -Fixed issues importing DRM-protected books -Fixed crashing issues on some tablet devices -Performance improvement -Other miscellaneous bug fixes'
